---
description: Auto-triggers structure-maintainer skill when project documentation, rules, or skill files change.
globs: CLAUDE.md, README.md, .cursor/rules/**/*.mdc, .cursor/skills/**/SKILL.md
alwaysApply: false
---

When any matching file is created or modified, read and follow the structure-maintainer skill:
- Skill file: `.cursor/skills/structure-maintainer/SKILL.md`
- Run the sync checklist to ensure CLAUDE.md, README.md, and all rules/skills are consistent
- Verify domain structure tables match the actual directory layout
- Check that new domains/sub-domains are reflected in documentation
